    "Nevertheless, the stem cell differentiation hierarchy driven by neurodevelopmental programs persists throughout tumor formation.",
    "DNA methylome analysis reveals genotype-dependent progressive changes of DNA methylation during gliomagenesis Tumor-cell DNA methylation was recently used for the molecular classification of brain tumors 6.",
